name: A new norm
description:
A New Norm represents a point at the journey toward a healthier sense of masculinity where I have become much more comfortable and adept at expressing myself emotionally and feeling as though I can rely on others.

The lone rose protruding from the mouth represents a significantly more controlled sense of verbal emotional expression. The thought of being vulnerable is no longer something that I fear, but find strength in.

36x48" Oil on Canvas.
